{"tid":1188036,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"［ 4月新番 ］ 進擊的巨人 Attack On Titan Season 3 Part.2（2）","createTime":"2019-06-06T04:14:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T06:23:40.000Z","uid":64894,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"396b4445c21d8d2aebe69d6b57d7266eeaa3b2d0","tid":1188036,"uid":64894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o9uRQ69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo9uRQ69.jpg&h=025fe6b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 歷經百年的時光，將人類與外側世界隔開的牆壁。在牆壁的另一側，似乎有前所未見的世界延伸開來。火焰之水、冰之大地、砂之雪原&hellip;&hellip;。記載在書中的，儘是些激發少年探究心的文字。在時間流轉，牆壁被巨人毀壞的現在，人類正一步步接近世界的真相。巨人的真實身份是什麼？為何牆壁中會埋著巨人？巨人化的艾連&middot;葉卡所持有的「坐標」之力是？以及，希絲特莉亞&middot;雷斯究竟知道這個世界的什麼事情？在艾連等 104 期兵的加入下，建立新體制的里維班。最強最惡的敵人，阻攔在開始行動的他們面前。<br />\n<br />\nSTAFF<br />\n原作：諫山創（別冊少年Magazine連載／講談社）<br />\n總監督：荒木哲郎<br />\n監督：肥塚正史<br />\n系列構成：小林靖子<br />\n角色設計：淺野恭司<br />\n音樂：澤野弘之<br />\n動畫製作：WIT STUDIO<br />\n <br />\nCAST<br />\n艾連：梶裕貴<br />\n米卡莎：石川由依<br />\n阿爾敏：井上麻里奈<br />\n柯尼：下野紘<br />\n莎夏：小林ゆう<br />\n克里斯塔：三上枝織<br />\n約翰：谷山紀章<br />\n萊納：細谷佳正<br />\n貝爾托特：橋詰知久<br />\n漢吉：朴璐美<br />\n艾爾文：小野大輔<br />\n里維：神谷浩史<br />\n吉克：子安武人<br />\n<br />\nPV<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fJm2nD3cv_4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfJm2nD3cv_4&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2Bgn9Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=98ecbeaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fJm2nD3cv_4</a>"},{"pid":"6bba68a46311a5aac63bfd96bb4809a2062f1079","tid":1188036,"uid":64894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:15:46.000Z","msg":"做咩一直都冇人開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://ebb.io/anime/146x627\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Febb.io%2Fanime%2F146x627&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2Bgn9Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=2521f03f\" target=\"_blank\">https://ebb.io/anime/146x627</